        <updateDate>2008-04-01T19:50:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Equitable Mineral Lease Revenue Sharing Restoration Act - Amends the Department of the Interior, Environment, and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2008, to repeal the requirement that the Secretary of the Interior deduct 2% from the amount payable to each state in FY2008, and deposit such amount to miscellaneous receipts of the Treasury.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
